  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Develop and evaluate a model of organization and management in the management of patients
      with cardiovascular risk factors (hypertension, diabetes mellitus, smoking, obesity, physical
      inactivity, dyslipidemia and family history) in primary care aimed at the compliance, control
      and treatment effectiveness.
    </textblock>
